es.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aThis eBook is made available Open Access under a CC BY-NC-ND 4.0 license: uhttps://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/4.0https://www.aup.nl/en/publish/open-access  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Jun 2022) 0aBazin, André,d1918-1958xCriticism and interpretation. 0aMotion picturesxPhilosophy. 0aMotion pictures. 4aFilm Studies. 4aFilm, Media, and Communication. 7aART / Film & Video.2bisacsh  aAndré Bazin, film criticism, realism, film language, film and other arts.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066152108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2019z9783110605785oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishz978311061001708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048542086?locatt=mode:legacyzOpen Access7040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048542086zOpen Access70423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048542086/original  a978-3-11-061001-7 EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5 EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-066152-1 Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DPKb2019  aZDB-23-GOA